 <sect1 id="sec.adm.docupdates.c4_gm">
  <title>August, 2014 (Initial Release &productname; 4)</title>
  <variablelist>
   <varlistentry>
    <term>Update to &ostack; Icehouse</term>
    <listitem>
     <para>
      <xref linkend="cha.adm.dash"/> and <xref linkend="cha.adm.cli"/> have been updated to the
      &ostack; Icehouse release on which &productname; 4 is based. This
      includes the following changes:
     </para>
     <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
      <para>All screenshots have been updated.</para>
     </listitem>
     <listitem>
      <para> Some categories have been added to the &dash;'s main screen,
       resulting in an update of the following section: <xref
        linkend="sec.adm.dash.intro.main"/>. </para>
     </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>The &dash;'s left navigation bar has changed slightly,
        triggering an update of all procedures mentioning how to access a
        certain screen.</para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>The following sections have been added to <xref
         linkend="cha.adm.dash"/>: </para>
       <itemizedlist>
        <listitem>
         <para>
          <xref linkend="sec.adm.dash.volumes"/>
         </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
         <para>
          <xref linkend="sec.adm.dash.hostaggr"/>
         </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
         <para>
          <xref linkend="sec.adm.dash.sysinfo.stats"/>
         </para>
        </listitem>
       </itemizedlist>
      </listitem>
     </itemizedlist>
     </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   </variablelist>
  </sect1>
 
 <sect1 id="sec.adm.docupdate.cloud3.maint1">
  <title>February 24, 2014 (Maintenance Release &productname; 3)</title>
  <!--state if new or updated, if applicable, add number of bug, fate,
   or doc comment for reference-->
  <variablelist>
   <varlistentry>
    <term>Image Management</term>
    <listitem>
     <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
       <para> Added example commands for all supported hypervisors to <xref
         linkend="pro.adm.cli.img.upload"/> and <xref
         linkend="pro.adm.cli.img.props.modify"/>.</para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>Documented how to set the image properties in a way that an
        uploaded image can be used for multiple hypervisors (&kvm;,
        &xen;, and &hyper;). See <xref
         linkend="tip.adm.img.req.virt.mult"/>.</para>
      </listitem>
     <listitem>
       <para>Removed special instructions for images built with &suseonsite;
        1.2 from <xref linkend="vl.adm.img.req.virt"/> and <xref
         linkend="pro.adm.cli.img.convert"/>. &suseonsite; 1.2 is
        discontinued, &suseonsite; 1.3 is the current version.</para>
     </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>Added a note to highlight the importance of setting image
        properties, especially when using mixed virtualization environments. See
         <xref linkend="sec.adm.dash.img"/> and <xref linkend="sec.adm.cli.img"
        />.</para></listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>Slightly reorganized <xref
        linkend="sec.adm.dash.img"/> and <xref linkend="sec.adm.cli.img"/>. Added more
        subsections for quicker overview.</para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   
   <varlistentry>
    <term>Bugfixes</term>
    <listitem>
     <para> Various improvements in <xref linkend="cha.adm.cli"/>
       (<ulink url="https://bugzilla.novell.com/show_bug.cgi?id=863876"/>).
     </para>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
  </sect1>
 <sect1 id="sec.adm.docupdate.cloud3.gm">
  <title>February 17, 2014 (Initial Release &productname; 3)</title>
  <!--state if new or updated, if applicable, add number of bug, fate,
   or doc comment for reference-->
  
  <variablelist>
   <varlistentry>
    <term>Update to &ostack; Havana</term>
    <listitem>
     <para>
      <xref linkend="cha.adm.dash"/> and <xref linkend="cha.adm.cli"/> have been updated to the
      &ostack; Havana release on which &productname; 3 is based. This
      includes the following changes:
     </para>
     <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
       <para>All screenshots have been updated.</para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para> Some categories have been added to the &dash;'s main screen,
        resulting in an update of the following section: <xref
         linkend="sec.adm.dash.intro.main"/>. </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para> The compute, memory, and storage capacity of some default flavors
        has slightly changed. For details, refer to <xref
         linkend="sec.adm.dash.flavors"/> or <xref linkend="sec.adm.cli.flavors"
        />. </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>There are more quota parameters available now. For details, refer
        to <xref linkend="sec.adm.dash.quotas"/> or <xref
         linkend="sec.adm.cli.quotas"/>.</para>
      </listitem>
      <!--taroth 2014-01-28: commenting because Keystone API v3 has been rejected for Cloud3
       as of today:
       <listitem>
       <para>The following procedures have been added to reflect the new
        features of &ostack; &o_ident; v3 API that are now supported in
        &productname; &dash;: <xref linkend="pro.adm.dash.user.roles"/>,
        <xref linkend="pro.adm.dash.user.groups"/>, and <xref
         linkend="pro.adm.dash.user.groups.assign"/>.</para>
      </listitem>-->
      <listitem>
       <para>It is now possible to modify flavors from the &productname;
        &dash;. For details, refer to <xref
         linkend="pro.adm.dash.flavors.modify"/>.</para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>Reflected package name change from <systemitem class="resource"
         >python-quantumclient</systemitem> to <systemitem class="resource"
         >python-neutronclient</systemitem>.</para>
      </listitem>
     </itemizedlist>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
    <term>Managing Networks</term>
    <listitem>
     <para>
      Added a section about managing networks to
      <xref
       linkend="cha.adm.cli"/>.
     </para>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
    <term>High-level User Roles</term>
    <listitem>
     <para>
      Added definition of user roles to
      <xref
       linkend="pre.cloud.admin"/>.
     </para>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
    <term>Offline and Live Migration of Instances</term>
    <listitem>
     <para>
      If a &compnode; needs to be shut down (for example, for a maintenance
      update), instances running on the &compnode; need to be migrated to
      another node. For details, refer to
      <xref
       linkend="sec.user.dash.migrate"/> and
      <xref linkend="sec.adm.cli.migrate"/>.
     </para>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   
   <varlistentry>
    <term>Bugfixes</term>
    <listitem>
     <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
     <para>Fixed typos in commands for showing and setting quota values for a
      project: <replaceable>PROJECT_ID</replaceable> must be used instead of
       <replaceable>PROJECT_NAME</replaceable> or
      <replaceable>PROJECT_ID_OR_NAME</replaceable>. See <xref
      linkend="sec.adm.cli.quotas"/>.</para>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
       <para>
        <xref linkend="vl.adm.img.req.virt"/>: Added image requirements for
        use with &vmware;
        (<ulink
         url="https://bugzilla.novell.com/show_bug.cgi?id=838040"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        <xref linkend="vl.adm.img.req.virt"/>: Added image requirements for
        use with &hyper;
        (<ulink
         url="https://bugzilla.novell.com/show_bug.cgi?id=836765"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        <xref linkend="pro.adm.cli.img.upload"/> and
        <xref
         linkend="pro.adm.cli.img.props.modify"/>: Added
        hypervisor-specific example commands for image upload and
        modification of image properties
        (<ulink url="https://bugzilla.novell.com/show_bug.cgi?id=838040"/>
        and
        <ulink url="https://bugzilla.novell.com/show_bug.cgi?id=836765"
        />).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        <xref linkend="tip.adm.img.req.virt.mult"/>: Added section on how to
        configure images for use with multiple hypervisors.
        (<ulink
         url="https://bugzilla.novell.com/show_bug.cgi?id=836765#c22"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>Fixed typos in commands for showing and setting quota values for a
        project: <replaceable>PROJECT_ID</replaceable> must be used instead of
        <replaceable>PROJECT_NAME</replaceable> or
        <replaceable>PROJECT_ID_OR_NAME</replaceable>. See <xref
         linkend="sec.adm.cli.quotas"/>.</para>
      </listitem>
     </itemizedlist>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
