 <sect1 id="sec.adm.docupdate.cloud2.gm">
  <title>September 11, 2013 (Initial Release &productname; 2.0)</title>

  <variablelist>
   <varlistentry>
    <term>&ostack; Service Names</term>
    <listitem>
<!--state if new or updated, if applicable, add number of bug, fate,
      or doc comment for reference-->
     <para>
      Replaced code names with the &ostack; services' real names, according
      to
      <ulink
        url="https://wiki.openstack.org/wiki/Documentation/Conventions#General_style_conventions"
       />.
      For example, talk of <emphasis>&ostack; &img;</emphasis> instead of
      <emphasis>&o_img;</emphasis>.
     </para>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
    <term>Update to &ostack; Grizzly</term>
    <listitem>
     <para>
      The &dash; and the command line chapter have been updated to the
      &ostack; Grizzly release on which &productname; 2.0 is based. This
      includes the following changes:
     </para>
     <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        The following section has been added:
        <xref
          linkend="sec.adm.dash.networks"/>.
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Some categories have been added to the &dash;'s main screen, others
        changed name. Most importantly, the download option for RC files can
        now be found in the <guimenu>Access &amp; Security</guimenu>
        category. See <xref linkend="sec.adm.dash.intro"/> and
        <xref
          linkend="sec.adm.cli.rc"/>.
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Image upload is now also possible via the &dash;, though with
        limited options. For details, refer to
        <xref linkend="sec.adm.dash.img"
         />.
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        The compute, memory, and storage capacity of the default flavors has
        changed. For details, refer to
        <xref linkend="sec.adm.dash.flavors"
         /> or
        <xref linkend="sec.adm.cli.flavors"/>.
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        The workflow for some tasks has changed, most notably for the
        following ones: <xref linkend="pro.adm.dash.user.create"/>, and
        <xref
          linkend="pro.adm.dash.user.assign"/>.
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        In addition to
        <xref linkend="vl.adm.img.req.general"
          xrefstyle="select:title nopage"/>,
        hypervisor-specific requirements have been added. Refer to
        <xref linkend="vl.adm.img.req.virt"/>.
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        &susestudio; and &suseonsite; now have better integration with
        &productname;. For details, refer to
        <xref
          linkend="sec.adm.cli.img.build"/>.
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        To make sure that an image is only launched on appropriate
        hypervisors, you can specify respective properties that the image
        requires. For details, refer to
        <xref
          linkend="pro.adm.cli.img.props.modify"/>.
       </para>
      </listitem>
     </itemizedlist>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
